cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.MM, cs.DB 

This paper is about image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of Bloom filters and compact hash codes suggests that the paper may also belong to the subfields of data structures (cs.DS) and database systems (cs.DB). Finally, the mention of mobile applications and distributed databases suggests that the paper may also belong to the subfield of multimedia systems (cs.MM).
